      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKEVIEW ZUMA (2) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, holding on for a minor placing when third and beaten 6 lengths at Warragul over 400m in 22.79. Can go on with it. POLLY GOLD (1) showed good early burn but run over late to finish 8th at this track in Maiden company. One of the main contenders. DR. TRACIE (3) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 0.8 lengths (24.55) behind Storm Coming at Traralgon. The form from her last run stacks up well. Must be included in calculations. GO HOME GIRL (7) is by Bernardo out of French Martini making debut. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Expected to produce a bold debut.",
